channel.title: [PI] Please help - how to stop a dupe that works on my server?
channel.description:
Okay recently, there has been partyhats everywhere on my server. And I received a PM from someone telling me how people are doing the dupe, they are using "Cheat engine 6.0", And they linked me to a youtube tutorial that shows you how to do the dupe here: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YaFWXTYcinI
I'm not sure How i would fix :(, I really need someones help if they could help me to patch this dupe i'll send them $5 Paypal.
If you are interested in helping me for paypal or for free, contact me on my msn: era@pk-era.com
Help is very much appreciated - thanks, Eraa
